{"id":170488,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-201184/","date":"2011-08-04T19:30:23Z","modified":"2011-08-04T19:30:23Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/8/4","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【动车相撞后续</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">】</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博商业周刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-04/china-rail-ministry-kingdom-may-be-split-up-on-fatal-crash.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的铁道王国可能会在致命事故后瓦解</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《中国争议》博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinadebate.com/2011/08/chinas-rail-disaster-and-the-great-leap-forward-mentality/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国铁路灾难和</span>“<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大跃进</span>”<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">心态</span> </a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110803/ap_on_re_as/as_china_train_crash\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">动车事故后，中国下令深化政务公</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">开</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《《雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110803/ap_on_re_as/as_china_human_rights\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国人权活动家呼吁释放王荔蕻，后者即将面临庭</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">审</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110804/wl_asia_afp/chinafoodsafety\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在食品安全大检查中逮捕了</span>2000<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">余</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人</span></a></span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/03/us-china-xinjiang-idUSTRE77238O20110803\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">喀什恐怖事件之后，汉族区街道空空，店铺关门</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——汉族不信任维族，维族不喜欢汉族</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《路透社》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110803/wl_nm/us_china_strike\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">杭州出租车罢工进入第三天，一些司机开</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">工</span></a></span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福克斯新闻》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foxnews.com/scitech/2011/08/03/massive-global-cyberattack-targeting-us-un-discovered-experts-blame-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对美国、联合国的大规模网络攻击</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">被</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">发现，专家指责中</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/blogs/dailychart/2011/08/chinas-one-child-policy?fsrc=scn/tw/te/dc/obrotherwhereartthou\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国严格的独生子女政策将带来什么</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《亚洲前哨》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=3360&#038;Itemid=422\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的能源紧缺开始发威</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——今年的中国能源危机为</span></span><span><span>2004</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年以来最大，已逐渐扩大到社会个领域，可能导致高耗能产业的大规模裁</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">员</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《国家利益》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nationalinterest.org/blog/paul-pillar/chinas-central-asian-problem-5695\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的中亚问题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国必须把反对恐怖主义和压迫一个主要的少数民族分开，而中国常常倾向于将之混为一谈</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/flashpoints-blog/2011/08/03/us-vs-china-undersea/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中美的海底较量</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>MIT</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的欧文</span></span><span><span>・</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">科特分析，中国的潜艇仅用于近海防御，但还是无法抵御美国潜艇的渗透</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/08/02/positive-steps-in-south-china-sea/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">沈丁立：</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">南海局势中的积极步骤</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——上月中国和东盟在巴厘岛协商同意了执行</span></span><span><span>2002</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年南海协议的行动准则，这是解决南中国海纷争的正确的一步</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教箴言报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/World/terrorism-security/2011/0803/Race-for-oil-heats-up-territorial-disputes-in-the-South-China-Sea\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">南中国海的领海之争随着油气开发竞争而加</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">剧</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110804/ap_on_re_as/as_china_japan\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国称日本防务报告不负责</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">任</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金砖四国》博客</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/kenrapoza/2011/08/03/in-europe-india-to-the-rescue/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度政府将寻求议会同意，提供</span>20<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元贷款缓解欧债危机</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋月刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/infocus/2011/08/inside-north-korea/100119/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在北朝</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">鲜</span> </a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（已有</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/141320/210510\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">译文</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/meast/08/03/syria.unrest/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">联合国安理会谴责叙利亚镇压抗议者，呼吁各方立即停止暴力</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《国家利益》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nationalinterest.org/commentary/balkan-war-redux-5696\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">巴尔干战火重现</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——种族暴力再次回到巴尔干，这次又让西方吃了一惊</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/meast/08/03/egypt.mubarak.trial/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">穆巴拉克带病在铁笼中受审</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他一度是阿拉伯世界独裁者的象征，周三出庭被指控杀害反政府示威者</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/kenrapoza/2011/08/02/china-downgrades-us-credit-rating-blames-political-parties/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国评级机构大公国际下调美国信用评级，指责两党政治</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福克斯新闻》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foxnews.com/world/2011/08/03/china-attacks-us-legislators-on-bringing-worlds-economy-to-brink/?test=latestnews\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国一边批评华盛顿处理债务不当，一边继续投资美国</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洞察中国》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinasignpost.com/2011/07/how-do-the-economic-outputs-of-china%E2%80%99s-8-most-productive-cities-compare-to-those-of-u-s-cities/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中美经济最发达八城市比</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">较</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111903885604576486153816151520.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国放松价格管制，食用油价格上</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">涨</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《上海人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://shanghaiist.com/2011/08/04/plaza_66_window_explodes_up_to_90_s.php\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">恒隆广场玻璃自爆，上海近</span>90%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的外墙玻璃不安</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">全</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/03/chinese-city-bans-pet-dogs\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为避免狂犬病，江门下令收缴扑杀</span>3<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万只狗</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：您可以到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>看到推友们对该篇译文的评论和转发；欢迎参与！如果您的电脑可以翻墙，请到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>的左栏参加我们的一个小调查</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-8318732903818101658?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":655,"categories":[1],"tags":[9553]}